					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9834102#post-4108858</guid>
				<title>Miracle treatment! Lose weight overnight!</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9834102/scp-4177#post-4108858</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 Jan 2019 02:28:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MaliceAforethought</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2902864</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I coldposted this as part of <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-381751">Bright's 24 Hour SCP Challenge</a>, wrote it extremely early in the morning, and the whole thing took about 4 hours from concept to posting. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546708235" alt="9Volt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" >9Volt</a></span> for inspiring me with <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3841">her own challenge entry</a>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546708235" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span> for inspiring me with a clickhole video, the title of which was the initial spark of inspiration I needed to write this scip. I've tried doing this challenge twice in the past, but this was the only one I made anything out of; here's hoping it succeeds.</p> <p>If you spot any grammar errors or poor wording, please let me know; my fatigue-addled brain does not too English goodspeak do.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
